org.apache.flink.api.common.typeinfo

类 Types

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.api.common.typeinfo.Types

  • @PublicEvolving
public class Types
extends java.lang.Object
    This class gives access to the type information of the most most common types.

    • 方法详细资料

      • ROW

        public static RowTypeInfo ROW(TypeInformation<?>... types)
        Generates a RowTypeInfo with fields of the given types. The fields have the default names (f0, f1, f2 ..).

        This method is a shortcut to new RowTypeInfo(types).

        参数:
        types - The types of the row fields, e.g., Types.STRING, Types.INT

      • ROW_NAMED

        public static RowTypeInfo ROW_NAMED(java.lang.String[] fieldNames,
                                    TypeInformation<?>... types)
        Generates a RowTypeInfo with fields of the given types and with given names.

        Example use: ROW_NAMED(new String[]{"name", "number"}, Types.STRING, Types.INT).

        This method is identical to new RowTypeInfo(types, names).

        参数:
        fieldNames - array of field names
        types - array of field types
